# Anki-workflow core

Read `AGENTS.md` and `workflow_status.md` before bulk work.

- Cards from `lectures/**/processed/**`, `lectures/**/cards/`, and `lectures/**/exam.md` only — not `raw/` PDFs
- Extract new PDFs with `batch_extract_course.py` before creating cards
- Backup via `scripts/backup_collection.py` before Anki imports >5 cards
- Lint via `scripts/lint_cards.py` before import; `--live` after import
- Permanent scripts in `scripts/`; ephemeral helpers in `scripts/_scratch/`
- Update `workflow_status.md` after extraction, import, or backup
- MC/TF: `anki_curated.json` (`type: mc|tf`) → `import_lecture_cards.py` → `import_mc_cards.py` (Add-on 1566095810); details in `AGENTS.md`
